{
  "chapter": 24,
  "chapter_summary": "玉骨魔挟持缪七娘与菁儿现身沙龙坪，以透骨断魂砂封锁毒圈，威胁无恨生交出无极岛。辛捷试图以虬枝剑法突破毒阵未果。毒君金一鹏突然出现，以无影之毒反杀玉骨魔，解救无恨生妻女。无恨生携妻女离去，辛捷埋葬玉骨魔尸身后，研读毒经。金氏兄弟赶至沙龙坪，辛捷告知毒圈危险。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_gu_mo",
      "speaker_name": "玉骨魔",
      "listener": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "text": "无极岛主，还识得我吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "无恨生",
      "listener": "char_yu_gu_mo",
      "text": "玉骨魔你手下那什么姓成的舵主真差劲啊，我本来还道东海海盗自从你老兄接管之后，一定威势大非昔比，哪里知道却是每况愈下，我做兄弟的看了真是失望得很，一气之下把三条船都送进了海龙王宫。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_gu_mo",
      "speaker_name": "玉骨魔",
      "listener": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "text": "就是因为我玉骨魔承海上兄弟瞧得起，尊称俺一声头儿，所以今日才来有一事求你老——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_gu_mo",
      "speaker_name": "玉骨魔",
      "listener": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "text": "你老也知道，咱们吃这行饭最重要的就是地盘，以前往来东海的船舶都得经过咱们十沙群岛，但是最近由于新发现航路，商人都绕道无极岛而行，这样咱们兄弟可就没有饭吃啦，所以在下斗胆敢请求无极岛主一桩事——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "无恨生",
      "listener": "char_yu_gu_mo",
      "text": "你可是要我无极岛作为你的地盘？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_gu_mo",
      "speaker_name": "玉骨魔",
      "listener": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "text": "不敢，不敢，在下只是请岛主赏咱们兄弟一口饭吃。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_gu_mo",
      "speaker_name": "玉骨魔",
      "listener": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "text": "咱们在黄子沙群岛另布置了一个小岛，一切住宅用具尽如无极岛原有的并无两样！如果岛主愿意的话，就请岛主屈住那里——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_gu_mo",
      "speaker_name": "玉骨魔",
      "listener": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "text": "无恨生，你且看一桩事物——",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "无恨生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "狂贼见招！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_gu_mo",
      "speaker_name": "玉骨魔",
      "listener": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "text": "无恨生大名久仰，何必再使这手功夫，只是这一截枯枝，算是答应还是不答——",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "无恨生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快退！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "无恨生",
      "listener": "char_yu_gu_mo",
      "text": "无恨生，我看你还是答允了吧！嘿嘿，论武功，我玉骨魔比你世外三仙差一筹，论毒，哈哈，我玉骨魔不客气要称一声举世无双——",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "金一鹏",
      "listener": "char_yu_gu_mo",
      "text": "什么人敢夸如此大口？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_gu_mo",
      "speaker_name": "玉骨魔",
      "listener": "char_jin_yi_peng",
      "text": "何方村夫竟到这里来撒野，快报上你猪名狗姓——",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yi_peng",
      "speaker_name": "金一鹏",
      "listener": "char_yu_gu_mo",
      "text": "老夫姓金，草字一鹏！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yi_peng",
      "speaker_name": "金一鹏",
      "listener": "char_yu_gu_mo",
      "text": "听你自夸毒器天下无双，哈哈，俺老儿第一个不服气——",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_gu_mo",
      "speaker_name": "玉骨魔",
      "listener": "char_jin_yi_peng",
      "text": "我玉骨魔不错说了这句话，你不服么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_gu_mo",
      "speaker_name": "玉骨魔",
      "listener": "char_jin_yi_peng",
      "text": "我玉骨魔足迹行遍海外穷岛僻野，哪一种奇毒异草没有见过，你们中原这等井底之蛙懂得些什么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yi_peng",
      "speaker_name": "金一鹏",
      "listener": "char_yu_gu_mo",
      "text": "我正奇怪怎么还有人敢在我金一鹏面前班门弄斧，原来阁下是蛮夷之族，那就难怪了，哈哈——",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_gu_mo",
      "speaker_name": "玉骨魔",
      "listener": "char_jin_yi_peng",
      "text": "好小子，算你有几分功夫，你可敢与我玉骨魔再赌命一次？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yi_peng",
      "speaker_name": "金一鹏",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "娃儿，你与我把那壶酒拿来——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_jin_yi_peng",
      "text": "金老前辈，酒来了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_gu_mo",
      "speaker_name": "玉骨魔",
      "listener": "char_jin_yi_peng",
      "text": "天上合我心意，老匹夫敢饮我一杯酒么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yi_peng",
      "speaker_name": "金一鹏",
      "listener": "char_yu_gu_mo",
      "text": "有何不敢？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_gu_mo",
      "speaker_name": "玉骨魔",
      "listener": "char_jin_yi_peng",
      "text": "告诉你也不妨，我在这酒中下有'立步断肠'，你若不敢喝下，现在求饶还来得及——",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yi_peng",
      "speaker_name": "金一鹏",
      "listener": "char_yu_gu_mo",
      "text": "你也敢饮我一杯么？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_gu_mo",
      "speaker_name": "玉骨魔",
      "listener": "char_jin_yi_peng",
      "text": "我劝老匹夫还是快去办后事——",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_er",
      "speaker_name": "菁儿",
      "listener": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "text": "爹！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_er",
      "speaker_name": "菁儿",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "啊！你——你——",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_jing_er",
      "text": "菁儿——等一等。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 389,
      "line_end": 389
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_shan_min",
      "speaker_name": "梅山民",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "捷儿，你认得她？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 393,
      "line_end": 393
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_shan_min",
      "speaker_name": "梅山民",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "捷儿，我看那'梅香剑'今夜就可大功告成了。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 399,
      "line_end": 399
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_mei_shan_min",
      "text": "梅叔叔，咱们先回家罢——",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 403,
      "line_end": 403
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_shan_min",
      "speaker_name": "梅山民",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "啊——对了，那玉骨魔曾下过什么'透骨断魂砂'，那一块土地三个时辰不可有人走动，现在捷儿你最好在这儿停一会儿吧，等那毒儿失效，千万不要使人误过！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 407,
      "line_end": 409
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这玉骨魔的尸身，我还是把他埋了吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 415,
      "line_end": 415
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_jin_yuan_bo",
      "text": "前进不得！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 481,
      "line_end": 481
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_jin_yuan_bo",
      "text": "且慢，那块地走不得——",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 487,
      "line_end": 487
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yuan_bo",
      "speaker_name": "金元伯",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "阁下是说，这块土地咱们不可以行走么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 489,
      "line_end": 491
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_jin_yuan_bo",
      "text": "啊，原来是金氏兄弟，是的，这土地上附有奇毒，饶是功夫高绝，也挡不住此透骨断魂砂。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 495,
      "line_end": 497
    }
  ],
